---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout 
  title="AI on Your Website: A Business Owner's Guide [2025]" 
  description="Expert guide to using AI on your business website. Learn where AI adds value, the pitfalls to avoid, and why it's not just 'adding ChatGPT'. Hampshire web design expertise."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-primary-50/30 to-primary-100/50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <span class="inline-block bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-6">
        2025 Business Guide
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
        AI on Your Website: <span class="text-primary-500">What Business Owners Need to Know</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        It's not just about adding ChatGPT. Learn where AI genuinely adds value to your website, 
        the expensive mistakes to avoid, and how to choose between local and cloud-based solutions.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="#where-to-use" class="bg-primary-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-600 transition-colors duration-200 font-semibold text-lg">
          Where to Use AI
        </a>
        <a href="#pitfalls" class="border-2 border-primary-500 text-primary-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors duration-200 font-semibold text-lg">
          Avoid the Pitfalls
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Introduction -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Every business owner has heard the hype: "Add AI to your website!" But here's what most 
        web agencies won't tell you: slapping a ChatGPT widget on your homepage is often worse 
        than useless—it can damage your credibility, slow your site down, and create legal liabilities 
        you never anticipated.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        As Hampshire-based web developers who've integrated AI into dozens of business websites, 
        we've seen what works and what fails spectacularly. This guide cuts through the marketing 
        fluff to show you where AI genuinely benefits your online presence—and where it actively 
        harms it.
      </p>
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-6 rounded-r-lg my-8">
        <p class="text-gray-800 font-medium">
          <strong>Key Insight:</strong> Using AI on your website is fundamentally different from using 
          ChatGPT for your emails. Website AI needs to be fast, reliable, secure, and aligned with 
          your brand—24/7, without hallucinating wrong information to your customers.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Big Difference -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">
        Website AI ≠ ChatGPT
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
            </svg>
            ChatGPT on Your Website
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-500">✗</span>
              Can give wrong answers about your business
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-500">✗</span>
              No control over what it says to customers
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-500">✗</span>
              Requires users to have their own account
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-500">✗</span>
              Data sent to OpenAI's servers
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-500">✗</span>
              Generic responses, not your brand voice
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-500">✗</span>
              No integration with your booking/cart systems
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            Proper Website AI Integration
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500">✓</span>
              Trained on your specific business data
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500">✓</span>
              Controlled responses with guardrails
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500">✓</span>
              Seamless for all visitors—no accounts needed
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500">✓</span>
              Can run locally (data stays on your server)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500">✓</span>
              Matches your brand voice and tone
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500">✓</span>
              Connects to your booking, payment, and CRM systems
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Where to Use AI -->
  <section id="where-to-use" class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">
        Where Should AI Actually Go on Your Website?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 text-center mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Strategic AI implementation delivers ROI. Random AI placement wastes money and frustrates users.
      </p>

      <!-- GOOD Uses -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
          ✓ High-Value AI Applications
        </h3>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">1. Smart Product Recommendations</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">
              "Customers who bought X also bought Y"—but actually intelligent, based on browsing patterns, 
              not just purchase history.
            </p>
            <p class="text-green-700 text-sm font-medium">
              ROI: 10-30% increase in average order value
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">2. Intelligent Search</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">
              Visitors type "blue widget for garage" and find the right product—even if your 
              descriptions don't use those exact words.
            </p>
            <p class="text-green-700 text-sm font-medium">
              ROI: 15-25% improvement in search-to-purchase conversion
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">3. Dynamic Pricing Optimization</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">
              Adjust pricing based on demand, competitor analysis, and inventory levels—automatically 
              and within rules you set.
            </p>
            <p class="text-green-700 text-sm font-medium">
              ROI: 5-12% margin improvement
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">4. Content Personalization</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">
              Show different homepage content to first-time visitors vs. returning customers 
              vs. abandoned cart users.
            </p>
            <p class="text-green-700 text-sm font-medium">
              ROI: 20-40% improvement in engagement
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">5. Chatbot with Business Context</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">
              Answers questions using your actual documentation—prices, availability, delivery times—
              not generic web knowledge.
            </p>
            <p class="text-green-700 text-sm font-medium">
              ROI: 30-50% reduction in support tickets
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">6. Automated Content Generation</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">
              Create location-specific landing pages, product descriptions, or SEO content 
              from data feeds—properly edited by humans.
            </p>
            <p class="text-green-700 text-sm font-medium">
              ROI: 70% reduction in content production time
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- BAD Uses -->
      <div id="pitfalls">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-700 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
          ✗ Expensive AI Mistakes (The Big NOs)
        </h3>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-600">NO:</span> Generic ChatGPT Chatbots
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-2">
              That "Ask our AI assistant!" popup that doesn't know your prices, can't check stock, 
              and hallucinates wrong answers about your services. Customers hate it.
            </p>
            <p class="text-red-700 text-sm font-medium">
              Cost: Lost customers + damaged reputation + potential legal liability
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-600">NO:</span> AI-Generated Images Without Disclosure
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-2">
              Using AI-generated photos of your "team" or "office" that don't exist. When customers 
              visit or video call and see something completely different, trust is destroyed.
            </p>
            <p class="text-red-700 text-sm font-medium">
              Cost: Complete loss of credibility when discovered
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-600">NO:</span> AI Writing All Your Content Unedited
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-2">
              Publishing AI-generated blog posts and service pages without human review. They often 
              contain subtle errors, outdated information, or just sound generic and soulless.
            </p>
            <p class="text-red-700 text-sm font-medium">
              Cost: Google penalises low-quality content; customers sense the inauthenticity
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-600">NO:</span> AI Making Pricing Decisions Unsupervised
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-2">
              Letting AI adjust prices without guardrails. Stories abound of algorithms pricing 
              products at £0.01 or 10x normal price during glitches.
            </p>
            <p class="text-red-700 text-sm font-medium">
              Cost: Revenue loss or customer outrage from price errors
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-600">NO:</span> Processing Sensitive Data Through Cloud AI
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-2">
              Sending customer medical records, financial details, or legal documents to external 
              AI services (OpenAI, Claude, etc.) without considering GDPR and data protection laws.
            </p>
            <p class="text-red-700 text-sm font-medium">
              Cost: GDPR fines up to 4% of annual revenue + legal liability
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Local vs Cloud Models -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">
        Local AI vs Cloud AI: The Critical Decision
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 text-center mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Where your AI runs affects speed, cost, privacy, and control. Choose wrong and you'll 
        face problems you never anticipated.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Cloud AI -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Cloud AI Models</h3>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 text-sm">
            OpenAI GPT-4, Claude, Gemini, etc. Your data goes to their servers.
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-700 mb-1">✓ Best For:</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>• General content generation</li>
                <li>• Non-sensitive customer queries</li>
                <li>• Prototyping and testing</li>
                <li>• When you need cutting-edge capabilities</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-700 mb-1">✗ Avoid For:</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>• Medical/health data</li>
                <li>• Financial records</li>
                <li>• Legal documents</li>
                <li>• GDPR-sensitive personal data</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-sm text-blue-800">
                <strong>Cost:</strong> Pay per token (usage). Can be £50-500/month depending on traffic.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Local AI -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Local AI Models</h3>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 text-sm">
            Self-hosted on your server. Models like Llama, Mistral, or fine-tuned open-source variants.
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-700 mb-1">✓ Best For:</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>• Sensitive data processing</li>
                <li>• High-volume operations</li>
                <li>• GDPR compliance requirements</li>
                <li>• Custom fine-tuned models</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-700 mb-1">✗ Challenges:</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>• Requires technical expertise</li>
                <li>• Server hardware costs</li>
                <li>• Not as capable as cloud models (yet)</li>
                <li>• Maintenance responsibility</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-green-50 p-3 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-sm text-green-800">
                <strong>Cost:</strong> Higher upfront, but flat monthly hosting fee regardless of usage.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Our Recommendation for Hampshire Businesses</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Most small businesses should start with <strong>cloud AI for non-sensitive tasks</strong> 
          (content suggestions, basic chatbots) and consider <strong>local AI only when processing 
          customer data</strong> or at significant scale. We help you make this decision based on 
          your specific industry and compliance requirements.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Choosing the Right Model -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">
        How We Choose the Right AI Model for Your Website
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-600">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Analyse Your Use Case</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Are you generating content? Answering customer questions? Analysing data? 
              Each task needs different capabilities. A model great for writing isn't necessarily 
              good for code or structured data extraction.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-600">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Data Sensitivity Assessment</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Does the AI need to process customer names? Order details? Medical info? 
              This determines whether cloud or local is appropriate—and which providers 
              can meet your compliance needs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-600">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Volume & Speed Requirements</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              10 queries per day? 10,000? Local models can be faster for high volumes 
              since there's no network latency. Cloud models often have rate limits that 
              can throttle your site during traffic spikes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-600">4</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Budget Reality Check</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Cloud AI seems cheap until you scale. A site with heavy chatbot usage can 
              rack up £1,000+/month in API fees. Local AI costs more upfront but is 
              predictable. We model both scenarios for you.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-600">5</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Test, Monitor, Adjust</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We never deploy AI and forget it. We track accuracy, response times, 
              and customer satisfaction. Models are upgraded, prompts are refined, 
              and guardrails are tightened based on real usage data.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Real Success Stories -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg-px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">
        Real Results: AI Done Right
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">E-commerce Site: 40% Revenue Increase</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
            Implemented AI-powered product recommendations and intelligent search for a Hampshire 
            retail business. The system learned from browsing patterns to suggest complementary products.
          </p>
          <p class="text-green-700 text-sm font-medium">
            Result: £12,000 additional monthly revenue after 3 months.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Service Business: 60% Fewer Support Calls</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
            Built a context-aware chatbot trained on the company's actual documentation. 
            It answers 80% of common questions without human intervention.
          </p>
          <p class="text-green-700 text-sm font-medium">
            Result: Owner reclaimed 15 hours/week previously spent on repetitive emails.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Local Trades: 25% More Enquiries</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
            Used AI to generate 50 location-specific landing pages for different service areas. 
            Each page was human-edited but AI-drafted from a data feed.
          </p>
          <p class="text-green-700 text-sm font-medium">
            Result: Dominated local search for "[service] + [town]" combinations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">GDPR-Compliant Local AI</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
            Implemented a self-hosted AI system for a healthcare-adjacent business. 
            All patient-adjacent data stays on their server, never leaves the UK.
          </p>
          <p class="text-green-700 text-sm font-medium">
            Result: Passed regulatory audit with zero data protection concerns.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Bottom Line -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
